要将旋转角度改为180度，您只需将代码中的 40 修改为 180。

修改后的代码如下：

```cpp
int join_line() {
    digitalWrite(LED_PIN, true);
    // line found, turn on the spot to line up.
    while (abs(kinematics.Theta) < 180*(3.14/180)) { // TURN ON THE SPOT TILL at 180 degrees, Allows our robot to get lined up enough for on line arc to take over.
        kinematics.update(); // need updated theta values.
        motors.setMotorPower(25, -20); // turn right for left sensor sees first
    }
    return(2); // once out of while loop, assume on line.
}
```

